title: Global Day of Coderetreat 2014 - Vienna, Austria
description:
Get your ticket here (it's free, we just ask for a deposit, which will be returned immediately to those showing up) - http://gdcr14-vienna.eventbrite.com (http://gdcr14-vienna.eventbrite.com/) 
Know others, your friends, peers at work, who might be interested too? Please, help spreading the word and tell them about our event. 
Looking forward to seeing you at the GDCR14 Vienna!
